## PropertyTypes type

Maps properties to their corresponding run-time types

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
export declare type PropertyTypes<T extends Record<string, unknown>> = {
    [P in keyof T]-?: Type<Exclude<T[P], undefined>>;
};
```
